{"tid":1429744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[軍工台] 7.8小更新 護目鏡&頭盔&手套更新數據","createTime":"2019-08-07T14:41:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T14:48:57.000Z","uid":105976,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"a1d4425389de178b35397fc591f4db0dfd648bf7","tid":1429744,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:41:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://forms.gle/XsqWzszYjBZkhzFc6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FXsqWzszYjBZkhzFc6&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=1067817c\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/XsqWzszYjBZkhzFc6</a><br />\n前線氣密護目鏡表現調查<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/9eN9YdpTwgxTGhAv8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F9eN9YdpTwgxTGhAv8&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=de5e27fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/9eN9YdpTwgxTGhAv8</a><br />\n頭盔調查表現調查</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>全防圖詳解&amp;購買連結 轉分頁  強烈建議睇 用pc開</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=616d4a19\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHI 又係我dgx<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">7.8更新</span></strong><br />\n*前線反映 6502QL 這款6200系列面罩 有快速戴/除功能 能增加前線機動性<br />\n 而且膠料更有彈性. 貼面更氣密  <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">5.8更新 </span></strong><br />\n*護目鏡條帶戴高D 通常鼻位GAP就會消失 (連唔連住豬嘴戴都係, 連住更好)<br />\n*Pyramex I-Force 護目鏡(非氣密) , 超高防撞規格 岩晒唔洗眼鏡既人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1411916/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1411916/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nA. 前線護目鏡初步實測數據 (因為d鏡都係岩岩運到無耐)<br />\nsample size係細D 但因為係前線戴住食彈 所以數據都算可靠 可參考<br />\n<br />\n(眼鏡係非必需既人 入面用泳鏡+ 外面加副防撞既護目鏡)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGyRm7B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGyRm7B.png&h=e2138560&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n1. Sellstrom Fire Goggles  S80225<br />\n4個人戴住 1個話完美 2個話少少漏氣可接受 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xCBb6z0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxCBb6z0.png&h=a01f020f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一般滑雪鏡 (通常都海棉邊, 非氣密, 有透氣孔)<br />\n效果不佳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SRAHtOX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSRAHtOX.png&h=a598d2c8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n3m 2890s<br />\n其實2890s冇話佢係氣密  所以效果差都係預計內<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nB. 頭盔數據<br />\n<br />\n1. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fQo6a2Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfQo6a2Z.jpg&h=95a08481&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地盔頭盔 被扑 都有50%係護到<br />\n被射 (有17位巴絲頭盔中彈)  2/3頭盔係會穿<br />\n大約一半人係唔太痛  另一半人就幾痛下<br />\n所以點都要戴頭盔 <br />\n<br />\n2. 單車盔 有6個人被扑頭 100%都話只有少少痛 效果幾好<br />\n但3個人被射中過 3個都穿左 2個幾痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nC.滅火隊裝備<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Li2VORT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLi2VORT.jpg&h=3df475af&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n得31%人有正規耐火耐熱手套<br />\n有40%人係用緊勞工手套   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而97%既人 入面係冇多副防化學既薄膠手套<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 正規耐火耐熱手套有90%人都話好 唔熱唔痛/普通 有少少熱<br />\n<br />\n3. 焗爐手套有90%人話係普通 有少少熱少少痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j0Ew6Fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj0Ew6Fe.jpg&h=239aadf8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n勞工手套  55%人話係勉強/差<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n超過400前線豬嘴實測應該好多人睇過 唔再詳講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1395831/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1395831/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"bd4993409dbfa2a68db9f3c420be3cb79b4f1314","tid":1429744,"uid":102535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:42:49.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"4486f0efa24f34e342f5e25dff6fc5edf0d0bff7","tid":1429744,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b043a0b4c00ab199f15d354bd8fe36ac2432fc1a","tid":1429744,"uid":268160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:56:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"684b2a23a4c99bbbdd70a67c1a36c6adf36c2f67","tid":1429744,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704fb8b6a6160935568fa91d2f3b48a06690e7ac","tid":1429744,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/fqHBJg6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfqHBJg6.jpg&h=7309e265&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/nKm3DBs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnKm3DBs.jpg&h=ae37b1f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9cd83084afc222856e7db63d122eb1d6fb715bf","tid":1429744,"uid":105976,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/frtU0Tb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fn